      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "629572",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "Drwinnie2",
        "uid": "80598"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\tWhy? Because the copy is the nature of Chinses high tech companies. There already have been Chinese versions of Google, Quaro, Wiki, Paypal, Boston Dynamics and a lot more. It makes so much sense to have Chinese version of ChatGPT.\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-02-09",
